{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Fallen Friendship, a Stolen Love\u2014</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To rescue his beloved, taken by a trusted friend, a vengeful shadow pierces the darkness in a high-speed, exhilarating running action game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cut Through Enemy Lines with &quot;Gale Rush&quot; !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the ultimate thrill with simple controls: just lock on and strike! Become a whirlwind, wielding lightning-fast sword techniques to carve through layers of fearsome foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/03.gif?t=1732594894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time is Running Out!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the moon sinks and the sun rises, the forbidden ritual &quot;Akegarasu&quot; will make it all too late. With only one minute until dawn, every slash with the secret technique &quot;Chronomancy&quot; extends the night. Fight against the clock until the very last second!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/02.gif?t=1732594894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic Actions to Overcome Obstacles!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash a wide array of high-speed, heroic moves straight from the pages of manga and anime. Leap over enemies and obstacles with flair, racing toward victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/extras/01.gif?t=1732594894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run Until the Final Moment!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732594894","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a